或她為何會出現在法庭，但對於裁定他或她是否犯了罪是沒有關聯的。」<br />\n<br />\n我們走進這位人權大狀，聽一聽他半輩子的法律堅持，看看他如何輸了一仗再打一仗&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3qE1DoI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3qE1DoI&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=36748a62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3qE1DoI</a><br />\n<br />\n#相關閱讀<br />\n大檢控，香港人經歷的拘捕和審判☞☞☞<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3fXMwAv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3fXMwAv&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=9ff79524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3fXMwAv</a><br />\n=============================================<br />\n😽一人限定、多人團購，暢閱不受限！ #學生方案：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bUODnu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bUODnu&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=2921aa04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3bUODnu</a><br />\n<br />\n😽用你選擇的媒體，決定你看見的世界 #加入會員：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2wVfM6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2wVfM6g&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=2886135d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2wVfM6g</a><br />\n<br />\n#端傳媒 #香港 #大律師 #司法獨立 #國家安全法 #反修例運動 #香港法治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T19:32:43.000Z","msg":"其實真正保護市民，得槍炮子彈"},{"pid":"f59a0963cc6916469b5f3874bf742b7049736198","tid":2317602,"uid":386200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b777bb822c724699a7ec4c5e02d545e6752067b","tid":2317602,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e10db5c9ff0413358303dddabd3e9d2760ba54cf","tid":2317602,"uid":245713,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e702ca946ab27db65c035805f9466907a6ca04","tid":2317602,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T17:27:30.000Z","msg":"佢要整死晒呢班人<br />\n又唔俾人離開香港<br />\n返工又政治打壓<br />\n眾籌幫手又告洗黑錢<br />\n<br />\n迫虎跳牆 人為咗生存<br />\n任何極端嘅事都做得出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T17:38:23.000Z","